<p class="eyebrow">Open Source</p>
<h1>Reference tools for the communications problems we solve in production.</h1>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel publishes libraries, modules, and security tools we build to run our own platform. Each project is dual-purpose: it solves a problem we have, and it's useful to anyone running similar infrastructure.</p>
